<br>
Is it correct that discounting buffs &amp; FT you regen mana at 1pt per tick standing? (I think I read that somewhere)<br>
<br>
Is it also correct that ignoring the meditation ability you get 2 or 3pts per tick sitting?<br>
<br>
If so then I think the question is do we get the 2pts of mana regen from sitting when using a horse or do we only get the meditation, FT and buff regen?<br>
<br>
Have I correctly paraphrased your question?<br>
<br>
